body.description: Terra Bamboo Baby Wipes with 99.5% Pure NZ Water and a hint of Manuka Honey are strong and durable, yet soft and fresh. The natural ingredients in our bamboo water wipes have been carefully selected to help even the most sensitive skin stay nourished and moisturized while protecting against rash and irritation. Terra All-Natural Sensitive Baby Wipes are 100% Biodegradable FSC Certified Bamboo Fiber, 0% Plastic or other Harsh Chemicals. Terra Baby Wipes are Unscented and perfect for baby’s sensitive skin. As with all wipes, these are not flushable baby wipes, however, Terra wipes are 100% compostable and biodegradable. Unlike other natural baby wipes, Terra biodegradable wipes are thick & durable, with an easy dispensing flip-top lid. Cross woven for a soft cloth-like texture that is non-irritating while cleaning baby's delicate skin. Infused with locally sourced MG350+ Manuka Honey, Terra all-natural baby wipes are rated ‘Excellent’ for all skin types by Dermatest and perfect for even the most sensitive newborn skin.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Terra's mission is to use the best of technology, design & nature to create innovative, sustainable products that can be trusted to work. Terra 100% Bamboo Baby Wipes are Perfect for Sensitive Skin! So strong but so fresh. The natural ingredients in Terra bamboo baby wipes have been carefully selected to help even the most sensitive skin stay nourished and moisturized while protecting against rash and irritation. Made from 100% FSC-Certified Bamboo (NOT from Viscose) and 99%+ Pure NZ Water. 0% Plastic, Chemicals, Fragrance, Optical Brighteners or Other Harsh Chemicals. All our products go through intensive testing so you can be sure that Terra water wipes is one of the purest and most natural baby wipes you will ever use. Gentle on your baby and their world.

Large & Textured for Durability Unlike other natural baby wipes, Terra wet wipes are thick, textured & durable to handle even the messiest situations! The soft, cross-woven cloth-like texture is non-irritating while cleaning baby's sensitive skin. Perfect for Everyday Use for all of Life's Messes! Terra sensitive water wipes are formulated for bums, faces, hands and all everyday messes at home and on the go. Great for parents and pets too! Never tested on animals. As with all baby wipes, these are not flushable. Terra 85% Plant-Based Diapers If you love Terra Baby Wipes, you'll definitely love Terra Diapers! They're 85% Plant-Based with 0% Chlorine, Fragrance, Latex, Parabens, Phthalates or Bleach. Not only are they better for baby, they provide up to 30% greater absorbency than leading diaper brands!

Three Different Types of Terra 100% Bamboo Baby Wipes Pure NZ Water Wipes TRANSPARENT INGREDIENTS: CLOTH: 100% Bio-degradable FSC Certified Bamboo Fiber (NOT Bamboo Viscose); 0% Plastic LIQUID: 99.7% Pure New Zealand Purified Water, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein Using crystal clear New Zealand water, our pure water wipes provide a naturally simple, yet nourishing cleanse for your baby. Complemented with soothing Aloe Vera and Vitamin E, these wipes are perfect for sensitive skin. Manuka Honey Baby Wipes TRANSPARENT INGREDIENTS: CLOTH: 100% Bio-degradable FSC Certified Bamboo Fiber (NOT Bamboo Viscose); 0% Plastic LIQUID: 99% Pure New Zealand Purified Water, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein, Organic MG650+ New Zealand Manuka Honey Terra Manuka Honey Wipes contain liquid gold that can only be produced in New Zealand. Our locally sourced MG650+ Manuka Honey is amazing for moisturizing with great anti-inflammatory effects, perfect for delicate, sensitive skin. Kiwifruit Extract Baby Wipes TRANSPARENT INGREDIENTS: CLOTH: 100% Bio-degradable FSC Certified Bamboo Fiber (NOT Bamboo Viscose); 0% Plastic LIQUID: 99% Pure New Zealand Purified Water, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein, Kiwifruit Extract As a New Zealand based business, we're no strangers to taking natural kiwi ingredients and making great products out of them. A staple in the New Zealand kitchen, kiwifruit is rich in vitamins and the extract provides natural moisturizing and cleansing benefits for your skin.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great wipe but do not dispense well
reviews.reviewText: The feel, durability, and no scent of these wipes are amazing. But they often do not come out one wipe at a time, which is extremely annoying. Other than that, these are wonderful wipes!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars BEST WIPES EVER
reviews.reviewText: I did a test using these wipes verses the honest brand. I will never go back. Don’t wait to buy this!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great wipes get the job done
reviews.reviewText: We have tried wipes by Pampers, Water Wipes, The Honest Company and All Clean eventually deciding to make Water Wipes our preferred brand.I thought the Terra wipes were good. They are relatively thick and textured so they reminded me of The Honest Company but I thought these were better, especially for messier clean-ups. I also felt like the wipes came out of the package easier versus accidentally pulling 5 wipes out instead of 1 or 2. I didn't notice a difference between the plain wipes and the Manuka honey ones.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Better then any water based wipe I've tried!
reviews.reviewText: These wipes were amazing! I love water based wipes so when I saw these, I was curious to try them out! Definitely not disappointed! I love that they are soft enough for any sensitive baby booty! And also wet enough for even the toughest diapers to change!! Great product! I will definitely be ordering again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Nice but pricey
reviews.reviewText: These wipes are nice enough. Good quality, thickness. Supposed to be septic system safe. The only issue is the price. They’re expensive. Price is the reason I won’t purchase again, but the profusely is nice.
